OL,3,CDistillery becomes first in the world
OL,4,Cto make blue gin using natural
OL,5,Cingredients
OL,7,FA distillery in Kent has become the
OL,8,Ffirst in the world to make blue gin
OL,9,Fusing natural ingredients.
OL,11,FMost gins have additives or colourants
OL,12,Fadded after the drink has been
OL,13,Fdistilled to give it its colour.
OL,15,FHowever, Copper Rivet in Chatham is
OL,16,Fturning the gin blue using an edible
OL,17,Fflower called the butterfly pea.
