OL,4,Cto make blue gin using natural
OL,5,Cingredients
OL,7,FThe man behind the new process is
OL,8,Fproduction manager Abhishek Banik who
OL,9,Fsays it's a "trial and error method"
OL,10,Fwhich is still being fine tuned.
OL,12,FThe distillery produces around 100,000
OL,13,Fbottles of gin and vodka per year with
OL,14,Fwhisky also on the list.
OL,16,FMost of it is sold across Kent, Surrey
OL,17,Fand Sussex, with markets also in the
OL,18,FEU, the US and Japan.
